column2: SELECT s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, ga.oiii_#_flux, ga.oiii_#_flux_err,sph.modelmag_u,sph.modelmag_g, sph.modelmag_r, sph.modelmag_i, sph.modelmag_z,   sph.subClass, g.petroRad_g,g.petroRad_u,g.petroRad_r,g.petroRad_i,g.petroRad_z, sph.z, sph.extinction_g,sph.extinction_u,sph.extinction_r,sph.extinction_z,   sph.extinction_i    INTO mydb.tremonti_#_ml  FROM GalSpecLine as ga, specobj as s, Galaxy as g, SpecPhoto as sph    WHERE ga.oiii_#_flux <#*ga.oiii_#_flux_err   AND s.class = &&&   AND s.specobjid = ga.specobjid   AND s.specobjid = g.specobjid    AND sph.specobjid = g.specobjid   AND sph.specobjid = ga.specobjid   AND ga.oiii_#_flux_err > #   AND g.specobjid > #   AND sph.z > #
